reviewText: Miss Spider is great! Nice, calm movie with good values. would give as a gift...we have alot of Miss Spider DVD's
Miss Spider is great! Nice, calm movie with good values. would give as a gift...we have alot of Miss Spider DVD's
My 3 year old grand daughter loves this movie.  Very well done!  Already own one other Miss Spider movie and will definitely buy more.

I had never heard of Miss Spider and the Sunny Patch Friends until my granddaughter requested everything Miss Spider for her birthday! I was amazed at the variety of stories and products I found.  She loved everything!! So if your little one is into Miss Spider she/he will enjoy this story as well.

My four month old son smiles and laughs when he sees them on the screen. Sometimes, it's the only thing that will keep him interested when he is fussy and I have tried every other option to sooth him. I like the buggies too, I must admit.. =)

My two year old loves the Miss Spider series.  I like that each episode is short but each dvd holds many episodes.  Most importantly, Miss Spider and her family reinforce our family's morals and values.  Healthy and loving family interactions show kids how brothers and sisters are supposed to be towards each other and how families should be towards others in their community.  "Be good to bugs- ALL bugs."  I highly recommend the Miss Spider movies to all families.
My son loves this dvd.  I must admit that I enjoy it myself.
These videos are often difficult to find, we were glad to add this one to our collection.

Miss Spider is the best childrens' series around in my opinion.  It has wonderful musical sequences, great stories, graphics, it educates children about the lives of bugs and how they interact in nature and it celebrates our earth in beautiful stories as well as presenting a lving family of natural and adopted bugs and how they live together.  My favorite too!  This DVD is wonderful, as are all the others in the series.

Or 2 1/2 year old loves Miss Spider! The segments move from one to the next without interruption for viewing ease. We love this series because our family was created thru adoption as was Miss Spider's.

My 4 year old daughter loves Miss Spider so when I heard that this DVD would be released; I was quick to pre-order it. All the episodes are great. The music and voices are so soothing. The storylines are good with wonderful values. As a mom, I am really impressed with this series. Hope there will be more to come on DVD!
Kids love them :)
My grandson was visitinf for summer vacation so I brought it for him to see if he would like it & he did. He loves it. He sings the songs & acts out parts
Very cute  my 3 year old son loves this show!
The book was in poor condition
Love all Miss Spider movies.

Both my kids who are 6.5 and 4 love this movie. The colors and story line are so beautifully done. They really enjoy it anytime they watch it, they love it so much that they watch it almost every day!!

My granddtr loved Miss Spider's Sunny Patch. She is 7 now n still watches it now n then. Her lil brother will be 2 soon. I bought new DVDs for him, n he loves them. He loves to dance to the music n these movies teach good lessons as well. Love the Sunny Patch movies.
The Miss Spider Sunny Patch series are great for the little ones. They teach life lessons in an effortless and enjoyable way.
I bought this for my niece. But every time she plays the dvd it freezes and then skips a portion of the movie. This happens many times.

For me... A Little weird and slightly kooky BUT my toddler Loves it..........  ?????
Guess we all have different outlooks at different stages of our lives.
